OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FA doctor told paranoid schizophrenic
OL,7,FValdo Calocane he could kill someone
OL,8,Fyears before he stabbed three people
OL,9,Fand attacked several others , the
OL,10,FNottingham attacks inquiry has heard.
OL,12,FCalocane killed students Barnaby
OL,13,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,14,F19, and grandfather Ian Coates, 65, in
OL,15,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023,
OL,16,Fbefore trying to kill three others
OL,17,Fwith a van.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
