OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry, which is looking into the
OL,7,Fevents leading up to the killings,
OL,8,Fheard that Calocane thought people
OL,9,Fwere trying to "invade" his mind,
OL,10,Fwatched videos about capital
OL,11,Fpunishment and mass shootings and sent
OL,12,Ftext messages about hurting people
OL,13,F"permanently" before he went on a
OL,14,Fviolent rampage.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@WO]uD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
