OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FToday it heard from consultant
OL,7,Fpsychiatrist Dr Faizal Seedat who
OL,8,Ftreated the killer at Highbury
OL,9,FHospital in Nottinghamshire where he
OL,10,Fwas detained under mental health laws
OL,11,Fon four occasions between 2020 and
OL,12,F2022.
OL,14,FCounsel to the Inquiry Rachel Langdale
OL,15,FKC asked Dr Seedat about a note which
OL,16,Fsaid Calocane had "no insight or
OL,17,Fremorse" about violent incidents
OL,18,Finvolving his neighbours, including
OL,19,Fone where a woman was severely
OL,20,Finjured, and "perhaps VC (Valdo
OL,21,FCalocane) will end up killing someone".
OL,26,@xD@SOUyD@HO]|D@NOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
