PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry previously heard that in
OL,7,FMay 2020, the former mechanical
OL,8,Fengineering student kicked repeatedly
OL,9,Fat a woman's door while experiencing
OL,10,Fpsychosis, causing her to jump from
OL,11,Fthe first floor window and break her
OL,12,Fspine.
OL,14,FDr Seedat told the inquiry: "I painted
OL,15,Fthe worst case scenario in terms of
OL,16,Fwhat could happen if he continued with
OL,17,Fhis behaviour.
OL,19,F"I reminded him that... next time, if
OL,20,Fyou continue this, that you would end
OL,21,Fup killing someone.
OL,26,@vD@]OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"So it was in that context to try and
OL,7,Fshock or highlight the importance of
OL,8,Fthe implications of his behaviours in
OL,9,Forder to try and help him start to
OL,10,Fdevelop some sort of understanding of
OL,11,Fthe gravity of the situation."
OL,13,FMs Langdale asked: "Did you think he
OL,14,Fcould end up killing someone?", to
OL,15,Fwhich Dr Seedat replied: "No, I
OL,16,Fdidn't."
OL,18,FHe told the inquiry: "When I said he
OL,19,Fwould kill someone, this would be
OL,20,Funintendedly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@^O]uD@TOUvD@^O]wD@ZOUxD@HO]zD@
OL,26,AVOU
