PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"If he went and did the same thing
OL,7,Fagain and somebody jumped out of the
OL,8,Fwindow and maybe they were on a higher
OL,9,Ffloor, the consequences could be very
OL,10,Fdifferent.
OL,12,F"And it was with that I meant that
OL,13,Fcomment ` not that he would kill
OL,14,Fsomeone physically by his hand."
OL,16,FMs Langdale put to Dr Seedat that an
OL,17,Femail he sent to a police officer
OL,18,Fabout Calocane's state of mind when he
OL,19,Fcaused the woman's injury in May 2020
OL,20,Fwas a "get out of jail free card".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@`O]|D@GOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
