OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry previously heard that
OL,7,FCalocane was not prosecuted over this
OL,8,Fincident because Dr Seedat told the
OL,9,Fofficer he was "not in touch with
OL,10,Freality".
OL,12,FDr Seedat told the inquiry: "On this
OL,13,Foccasion, I read the email as Pc
OL,14,F(Richard) Marsden asking whether I
OL,15,Fconcurred with the opinion that Valdo
OL,16,Flacked capacity at the time of
OL,17,Fcommitting the crime.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@HO]tD@]OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"I was never under the impression that
OL,7,Fit could be used to decide whether VC
OL,8,Fwas going to be charged or not
OL,9,Fcharged, and that was not my intention
OL,10,Fof sending that email."
OL,12,FDr Seedat wrote in the email that
OL,13,FCalocane had no recollection of the
OL,14,Fincident, but the doctor told the
OL,15,Finquiry that "at times he would say he
OL,16,Fdidn't remember the incidents and
OL,17,Fother times he said that he did".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]wD@NOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
