OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FChairwoman Deborah Taylor heard that
OL,7,FCalocane sent a series of text
OL,8,Fmessages in 2020 in which he talked
OL,9,Fabout "red rum", which is murder
OL,10,Fbackwards, and about wanting to hurt
OL,11,F"permanently".
OL,13,FHe also watched videos of mass
OL,14,Fshootings, including one of an attack
OL,15,Fin Buffalo, New York, and viewed
OL,16,Fdocuments related to police powers
OL,17,Fyears before he carried out the
OL,18,Fattacks in Nottingham.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@OO]sD@AOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
