PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1777050358
OL,3,CDoctor told Calocane he could kill
OL,4,Csomeone years before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,7,Fand three counts of attempted murder,
OL,8,Fis detained indefinitely in a high-
OL,9,Fsecurity hospital after prosecutors
OL,10,Faccepted his not guilty pleas to
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
